"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-simon-biles-2-vault-olympics-2024-gymnastics-yurchenko-b2589382.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Yurchenko double-pike is the latest in a string of signature moves innovated by Simone Biles  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 220, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Simone Bilesis back andas good as everat the ParisOlympics, three years on from a devastating case ofthe \\\"twisties\\\" in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 563, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999528290584, \"rank\": 4.709566027087312e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was forced to withdraw from several events at the 2020 Games after suffering the strange sensation in which a gymnast's mind and body no longer feel connected and a sense of disorientation prevents them from performing complex twists and spins through the air.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After taking time out from the sport to address her mental health, and seeking therapy to confront the trauma of sexual abuse at thehands of Larry Nassar, Biles has returned to gymnastics on a mission to prove to herself that she can overcome the hold the abuse had over her skills.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9999999733472581, \"rank\": 2.6652826876776735e-08, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles wowed crowds at the Bercy Arena in Paris this week - and millions more around the world - with a historic first, delivering her astonishing \\\"Biles II\\\" on the vault.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.6627330233574573e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The skill can also be performed on the floor, although the vault edition is the most eye-catching giving its sheer height and speed.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here, Biles' trademark skills are explained.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was just a teenager and recently minted national champion when Biles performed a tumbling pass at the 2013 world championships that she completes by doing a double layout with a half-twist at the end.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The move looks dangerous - Biles is essentially flying blind - but she and former coach Aimee Boorman came up with it because it was less taxing on her legs.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Boorman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aimee Boorman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Boorman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Boorman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was almost kind of necessity is the mother of invention,\\\" Boorman told The Associated Press in 2015.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999994124664, \"rank\": 5.873187831828492e-10, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her calf was hurting.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had bone spurs in her ankles and she's really good at floor with landings.\\\"\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles returned to the sport in 2018 following a two-year layoff after winning the all-around at the 2016 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not content to merely repeat herself, Biles began working on a triple-twisting, double flip that is now known simply as \\\" the triple-double.\\\"\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She unveiled it while winning the 2019 U.S. Championships then did it again at the world championships a few months later when she won the fifth of her record six world all-around titles.\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to see how it looked,\\\" she explained afterward.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As with a lot of gymnastics elements, Biles took a Cheng vault and added another layer of difficulty - this one an extra half twist on a vault originally done by China's Cheng Fei.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2716, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9998223892234128, \"rank\": 0.00012462381189271785, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheng_Fei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cheng Fei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheng_Fei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheng_Fei\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vault requires Biles to do a round-off onto the vault, then a half-twist onto the table before doing two full twists.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It entered the Code after she made it part of her routine at the 2018 world championships.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am embarrassed to do floor and vault after something like that,\\\" U.S. men's gymnast Yul Moldauer said in 2018.\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 3063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998167754879, \"rank\": 1.2140607845817723e-07, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3037, \"end\": 3049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yul_Moldauer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yul Moldauer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yul_Moldauer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yul_Moldauer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You see Simone do that and she's smiling the whole time.\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How does she do that?\\\"\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may be the most dazzling, most daring one of them all.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Yurchenko double pike had never been completed by a woman in competition, and few men have even tried.\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She began tinkering with it in 2021, but it's in the last year that it has morphed into perhaps the most show-stopping thing done in the sport.\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The vault asks Biles to do a round-off back handspring onto the table, then two backward flips in pike position with her hands essentially clasped to her knees.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She does it with so much power, she can sometimes overcook it.\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the U.S. Olympic trials last month, it drew a standing ovation.\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No, it's not normal,\\\" longtime coach Laurent Landi said after she drilled it at the 2023 U.S. Championships.\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3789, \"end\": 3802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Landi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's not normal.\\\"\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For all of her explosive tumbling, Biles is a wonder on balance beam, too, where she can make doing intricate moves on a four-inch-wide piece of wood seem almost casual.\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 4051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The same year she debuted the triple-double on floor, she added a double-twisting, double-tucked dismount off the beam.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She stuck it at the 2019 world championships, though she has since taken it out of her repetoire.\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The skill Biles submitted requires her to do a forward circle around the lower bar before turning a handstand into a 540-degree pirouette.\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Gymnastics teased the move on X on Friday.\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4411, \"end\": 4425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.994464000626658e-18, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bars is considered the weakest of Biles' events in the sense that just one of her 37 Olympic and world championship medals have come on bars.\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans even considered having Biles sit out bars during the team finals.\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4601, \"end\": 4614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1446615885582243e-16, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's slated to compete there Tuesday, though, and could unveil the skill there.\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additional reporting by AP  Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 5021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4787, \"end\": 4789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.2364429698322397e-13, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 4842, \"end\": 4853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.667836365642735e-20, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"